<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA61">
<l>paṇṭellām vēṅkaṭam pāṟkaṭal vaikuntaṅ</l>
<l>koṇṭaṅ kuṟaivārkkuk kōyilpōl – vaṇṭu</l>
<l>vaḷaṅkiḷaru nīḷcōlai vaṇpūṅ kaṭikai</l>
<l>yiḷaṅkumaraṉ ṟaṉviṇ ṇakar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As in all earlier times Vēṅkaṭam, the milk ocean [and] Vaikuntam</l>
<l>were the temples for him who took [them and] dwelled there,</l>
<l>[so now is] Kaṭikai, with lush flowers in long groves where a wealth of bees</l>
<l>rises, the heavenly city for the young prince.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
